{"tid":1180904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有豬農業界表示將登報譴責中國把關不力　冀加強檢疫","createTime":"2019-06-01T07:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T09:27:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7301669f61523599897b6e77dffdc1a4f5f20769","tid":1180904,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1460456_1_L_20190601150921.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1460456_1_L_20190601150921.jpg&h=bffb9d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水屠房再發現豬隻感染非洲豬瘟病毒，約4700隻豬需要全部銷毀。<br />\n<br />\n香港農業聯合會早上開會，商討如何應對。主席陳建業表示，將會登報譴責內地政府把關不力，期望內地質檢總局加緊檢驗檢疫，調查供港豬場是否有非洲豬瘟病毒。<br />\n<br />\n陳建業說，按規定豬隻到屠房後，3天內必須屠宰，但是次發現非洲豬瘟病毒的豬隻在上水屠房逗留6天仍未屠宰，批評屠房屠宰效率低、特區政府管理不力，將透過漁農界立法會議員何俊賢約見食衞局官員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460456-20190601.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460456-20190601.htm&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbVKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=96791c22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1460456-20190601.htm&h=b6a93a3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1460456-20190601.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1b17a6e1a95056bcf5305d7c50a5eddbc86db249","tid":1180904,"uid":163350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2be836a4eee117a3f449862f216692e3d1e33f2","tid":1180904,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"港豬獨?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a4dd2077bf02481d8d2e36a2123b7f2d92ce2f","tid":1180904,"uid":54721,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T07:58:17.000Z","msg":"佢就係要消滅香港養豬業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 